<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وقَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٧٧:</span> <span class="c3">{المَاعُونَ}</span>: المَعْرُوفَ كُلُّهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ بَعْضُ العَرَبِ:</span> <span class="c3">{المَاعُونَ}</span>: المَاءُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ عِكْرِمَةُ:</span> أَعْلَاهَا: الزَّكَاةُ المَفْرُوضَةُ،<span class="c5"> وَأَدْنَاهَا:</span> عَارِيَّةُ المَتَاعِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>